Patriot Gold Corp.


            
            Patriot Gold Corp. engages in the exploration and development of gold and other mineral resources. It projects include the Moss Mine, Bruner, and Vernal properties. The company was founded on November 30, 1998 and is headquartered in Las Vegas, NV.

            
